1
00:00:28,320 --> 00:00:29,240
Master Rak.

2
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:42,440
My apologies.

3
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,480
I'm cold.

4
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:30,820
I will serve you forever, Master Rak.

5
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:37,520
Your precious heart in my care...

6
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:40,520
I shall never allow it to be marred.

7
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,960
Saen...

8
00:01:56,540 --> 00:01:58,120
Do you know...

9
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:03,280
when I'm with you,

10
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:07,680
nowhere else in the world
feels as peaceful.

11
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,920
This life...

12
00:02:40,180 --> 00:02:44,680
asks no more
than to serve and be with my master.

13
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:50,680
I hope that in our next lives
we are of equal standing.

14
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:55,000
I could never...

15
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:00,800
push you away.

16
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:41,480
[Tanakorn Chuen-arom as Saen/Sand]

17
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:46,240
[Wacharathon Wongyai as Rak/Lucky]

18
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:50,360
[Worachai Areewong is Tan/Thank]

19
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:55,440
[Khitaphat Choothai as Chim/Charm]

20
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:59,040
[Kornkamon Supaseripap as Vila/ViVi]

21
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:03,300
[Rungtiva Sangngoen as Prink
Napat Seela as Rit/Ton]

22
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:06,880
[Chalisa Schaub as Kamala
Weeraachai Hatgovit as Phraya Banleng]

23
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:11,240
[Nithiroj Simakamtorn as Phraya Dechanarong
Rattanachai Phakdirat as Khon Master]

24
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,520
Every movement

25
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,800
our masters devised

26
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:31,760
was hard-won.

27
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,270
Go take a break.

28
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,480
We'll continue later.

29
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,920
Thanks a lot. See you.

30
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,800
[Khon Club Performance]

31
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:46,880
Hey!

32
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,880
Let me join the club.

33
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:53,400
I'm the real Thotsakan.

34
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,920
Are you?

35
00:04:59,420 --> 00:05:00,640
Do you know the basics?

36
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:02,840
Nope.

37
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:04,360
But I can try.

38
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:07,360
And I was born to be Thotsakan.

39
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,040
Khon is not a toy.

40
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:15,760
You can't just wear the mask
and randomly move your arms.

41
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,160
Then teach me.

42
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,320
You'll see I'm the right one for Thotsakan.

43
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,000
Sure.

44
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,960
Meet me tomorrow morning.

45
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:31,440
Seven sharp in the club room.

46
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,520
Okay.

47
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,040
Don't back out.

48
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,240
Me?

49
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,320
Don't run once you see the real thing.

50
00:05:45,840 --> 00:05:46,760
Stop!

51
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,180
Don't touch.

52
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:53,480
You'll go blind.

53
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,160
Go blind?

54
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,670
Superstitious much?

55
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,000
It's not superstition.

56
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:02,200
It's respect.

57
00:06:03,020 --> 00:06:04,800
Each Khon mask has its own master.

58
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,920
You must not disrespect it.

59
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,280
You want to get going?

60
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,310
Didn't you say
you wanted to be Thotsakan?

61
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,720
Yes, I do.

62
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:19,050
I wanna know how hard it could be.

63
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,320
Are you serious?!

64
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,000
If you can't handle this,

65
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:33,460
do you still think you can be Thotsakan?

66
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:35,880
Doing this and acting cool

67
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,760
doesn't mean you can teach Khon!

68
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:41,800
But that means I understand Khon

69
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:44,360
better than someone
who treats it like a joke.

70
00:06:57,700 --> 00:06:59,440
Then teach me Khon for real!

71
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:01,590
Stop playing around!

72
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,200
Who said I'm playing around?

73
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:06,200
This is basic Khon training.

74
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:08,280
Without faith,

75
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:10,920
you will never truly understand Khon!

76
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:20,280
Then you can have
your real Khon and shove it!

77
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,040
Good.

78
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,360
If you can't handle this,

79
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:30,760
go ahead and leave my club.

80
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,920
Get out!

81
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:51,040
May today's performance go smoothly.

82
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,960
Sadhu.

83
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,600
I need to poop.

84
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,920
That was fast, geez!

85
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:52,530
Thanks.

86
00:08:53,530 --> 00:08:55,170
That worked out better than I thought.

87
00:09:22,610 --> 00:09:23,610
You ready, Ton?

88
00:09:27,890 --> 00:09:29,050
Stay mindful.

89
00:09:29,730 --> 00:09:31,010
Don't make a mistake.

90
00:09:46,690 --> 00:09:48,970
[Khon Club Performance 2025,
Fadarun School]

91
00:10:53,690 --> 00:10:54,570
You!

92
00:10:55,890 --> 00:10:57,050
What the hell are you doing?

93
00:10:58,650 --> 00:10:59,810
I'm performing.

94
00:10:59,850 --> 00:11:02,890
Your Khon dancing is so stiff
it's painful to watch.

95
00:11:07,930 --> 00:11:09,610
You've ruined the performance.

96
00:11:11,570 --> 00:11:13,290
You've disrespected the masters.

97
00:11:14,130 --> 00:11:15,810
Don't you realize

98
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:17,770
this isn't just some ordinary show?

99
00:11:18,670 --> 00:11:19,610
I do.

100
00:11:20,090 --> 00:11:22,090
And I know that if this keeps going,

101
00:11:22,490 --> 00:11:23,570
nobody will care anymore!

102
00:11:23,610 --> 00:11:25,330
You have no right to talk about Khon

103
00:11:25,490 --> 00:11:28,770
when you have absolutely no clue
what it is truly about!

104
00:11:28,810 --> 00:11:30,210
That's exactly why...

105
00:11:31,290 --> 00:11:32,930
I'm making it easier to understand!

106
00:11:33,690 --> 00:11:34,890
Just wait and see.

107
00:11:35,930 --> 00:11:37,570
I'll make my own version of Khon

108
00:11:37,690 --> 00:11:39,450
and bring your club down!

109
00:11:47,970 --> 00:11:48,890
Rit!

110
00:11:49,170 --> 00:11:50,370
What have you done?!

111
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:51,810
Disgraceful!

112
00:11:52,730 --> 00:11:55,610
My son and servant
committed fornication under my roof!

113
00:11:56,690 --> 00:11:58,350
Prink and I are in love.

114
00:11:58,850 --> 00:12:00,610
And she's carrying your grandchild!

115
00:12:00,650 --> 00:12:02,250
Please stop!

116
00:12:03,290 --> 00:12:04,330
She's with child.

117
00:12:04,370 --> 00:12:05,250
Let her go!

118
00:12:05,290 --> 00:12:06,650
That's our grandchild!

119
00:12:07,050 --> 00:12:07,930
Silence!

120
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:09,370
I refuse to acknowledge it!

121
00:12:09,650 --> 00:12:10,570
Release her!

122
00:12:11,090 --> 00:12:12,210
Rit!

123
00:12:12,450 --> 00:12:13,290
You!

124
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:16,730
Saen!

125
00:12:17,690 --> 00:12:18,570
Saen...

126
00:12:19,010 --> 00:12:19,930
Are you well?

127
00:12:24,810 --> 00:12:26,010
Please don't punish Master Rit.

128
00:12:26,650 --> 00:12:27,890
Don't punish his child.

129
00:12:28,170 --> 00:12:29,410
Release me!

130
00:12:29,450 --> 00:12:31,130
Punish me in his place.

131
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:33,650
Please don't do this, my lord.

132
00:12:33,690 --> 00:12:34,650
Release me!

133
00:12:34,690 --> 00:12:36,450
Please don't do it. It's a sin.

134
00:12:37,650 --> 00:12:38,920
It's a sin.

135
00:12:40,050 --> 00:12:41,890
Take her away to be whipped.

136
00:12:41,930 --> 00:12:43,690
Teach her her place.

137
00:12:44,210 --> 00:12:45,930
And have Rit locked up.

138
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:47,770
He shall never see another soul again!

139
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:48,410
Prink!

140
00:12:48,450 --> 00:12:49,490
Master Rit!

141
00:12:49,530 --> 00:12:50,530
Prink!

142
00:12:50,570 --> 00:12:51,390
Master Rit...

143
00:12:51,430 --> 00:12:52,370
Prink!!

144
00:12:53,610 --> 00:12:54,610
Prink!!

145
00:12:55,830 --> 00:12:56,830
Prink!!

146
00:13:11,610 --> 00:13:14,450
Was it you who told Father?

147
00:13:14,850 --> 00:13:16,050
Traitor!

148
00:13:17,890 --> 00:13:19,370
No, I did not.

149
00:13:19,410 --> 00:13:20,690
I did not dare.

150
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:32,530
Leave us.

151
00:13:43,850 --> 00:13:45,490
Mother asked me to see you.

152
00:13:45,970 --> 00:13:47,170
She is worried.

153
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:52,250
You have neither eaten nor slept
for many days.

154
00:13:55,610 --> 00:13:56,610
Saen.

155
00:13:57,190 --> 00:13:58,490
I need to speak with you.

156
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:30,850
[Phranluang School]

157
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:43,330
In a few days, I am to perform Khon
before Phraya Dechanarong.

158
00:14:44,650 --> 00:14:46,290
I ask that

159
00:14:46,330 --> 00:14:48,650
you wear the Thotsakan mask in my place.

160
00:14:53,610 --> 00:14:56,730
When that day comes,
I shall run away with Prink.

161
00:15:05,490 --> 00:15:06,930
I...

162
00:15:07,890 --> 00:15:09,050
shall help.

163
00:15:33,130 --> 00:15:34,130
Saen.

164
00:15:34,810 --> 00:15:35,970
What are you doing?

165
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:37,970
Have you gone mad?

166
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:46,890
Those movements...

167
00:15:47,330 --> 00:15:49,170
are most certainly not Rit's.

168
00:15:58,010 --> 00:15:59,010
Stop!

169
00:16:17,190 --> 00:16:18,050
Prink.

170
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:19,820
Prink.

171
00:16:21,070 --> 00:16:21,950
Prink.

172
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:34,430
Master Rit, you should not be here.

173
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:38,900
I cannot stand by.

174
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:41,180
If we remain beneath this roof,

175
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:42,540
you will die,

176
00:16:42,700 --> 00:16:44,150
and I shall be dead while yet alive.

177
00:16:45,900 --> 00:16:47,940
A servant's life such as mine

178
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:51,100
is hardly a beautiful one.

179
00:16:53,260 --> 00:16:55,340
How could you remain with one such as I?

180
00:16:56,860 --> 00:16:59,220
I should not let you suffer with me.

181
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:00,660
And yet I will.

182
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:02,900
I can endure anything,

183
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:05,860
so long as I am with you.

184
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:14,420
We shall make our escape,

185
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:17,060
whatever the cost.

186
00:17:34,980 --> 00:17:35,980
Rit...

187
00:17:36,860 --> 00:17:38,140
Are you truly Rit?

188
00:17:49,500 --> 00:17:50,500
Rit...

189
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:52,820
He has taken ill.

190
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,580
He grows faint and unsteady.

191
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:01,340
I fear he may faint.

192
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,780
I should bring him inside to rest.

193
00:18:05,580 --> 00:18:07,220
If you grow faint or dizzy,

194
00:18:07,460 --> 00:18:09,040
remove the mask at once.

195
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:10,720
Why persist in wearing it?

196
00:18:12,780 --> 00:18:17,380
I do not think
he would prefer that at the moment.

197
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:20,740
What about when we return?

198
00:18:22,020 --> 00:18:23,860
Remove your mask at once!

199
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:43,460
Saen!!

200
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,420
I must apologize.

201
00:18:47,860 --> 00:18:50,980
Where is your wretched master?!

202
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,040
Go home at once!!

203
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:56,220
Do not let him get away!!

204
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,740
How dare you!

205
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,140
I alone shall take the blame.

206
00:19:26,260 --> 00:19:29,140
That is not your decision to make!

207
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:31,900
I asked you where your master is!

208
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:35,380
I do not know.

209
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:37,260
Father.

210
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,380
- Saen may...
- Rak!

211
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:42,700
Do you know where your brother went?

212
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:43,780
Master Rak knows nothing of it.

213
00:19:43,820 --> 00:19:45,260
I asked my son!!

214
00:19:45,460 --> 00:19:46,940
Not you!!

215
00:19:50,580 --> 00:19:51,980
Do not intervene!

216
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:54,980
Bind him and lock him in here!

217
00:19:55,020 --> 00:19:56,420
Take Rak away!!

218
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,540
Release me!

219
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:00,740
Saen!

220
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,740
- Saen!
- Rak!

221
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:31,780
Get out. All of you.

222
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:35,060
Do not let anyone in until I say otherwise.

223
00:21:15,220 --> 00:21:16,500
Saen...

224
00:21:18,780 --> 00:21:20,620
Look how badly they have hurt you.

225
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:35,540
I apologize for what I've done.

226
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:45,960
Does it hurt?

227
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:50,820
Why did you do it?

228
00:21:57,960 --> 00:22:00,340
Master Rit's child is important as well.

229
00:22:04,020 --> 00:22:07,020
I fear the child
will grow up without a father.

230
00:22:13,860 --> 00:22:17,340
To perform as Thotsakan

231
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:20,540
for my brother...

232
00:22:23,500 --> 00:22:25,300
how could you agree to it?

233
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:31,980
I was willing to.
